Home/Water Gardens/Aeration 




Aeration





×
Videos





Close




Aeration systems promote oxygen which is the lifeline to every ecosystem. With a bottom diffused aeration, water is circulated to increase dissolved oxygen levels. Water garden aerators can also be used in the winter months to keep a hole open in the ice.
Learn More







