Peter B. Pond, Chairman of the Board



Profile
Connections






Biography



    Peter B. Pond has served as one of our directors since 1997 and as Chairman of the Board since 2001. Mr. Pond is a founder of ALTA Equity Partners LLC, a venture capital firm, and has been a General Partner of that firm since June 2000. Prior to that, Mr. Pond was a Principal and Managing Director in the Investment Banking Department at Donaldson, Lufkin & Jenrette Securities Corporation in Chicago and was head of that company's Midwest Investment Banking Group. Mr. Pond holds a B.S. in Economics from Williams College and an M.B.A. in Finance from the University of Chicago. Mr. Pond served as a director of Navigant Consulting, Inc. from 1996 to 2014.
    





Board Membership




Peter B. Pond is not a member of any boards




 


  













